1. Get a craving for pizza
2. Figure out what pizza company you want
3. Google pizza company website
4. Customize pizza order
5. Purchase pizza
6. Wait for delivery
7. Check pizza box for correct order
8. Tip delivery person
9. Eat pizza

Additional 10. If order is wrong, check receipt for pizza co ph #
Additional 11. Contact pizza co and explain situation
Addtional 12. Receive refund or eat free pizza or return pizza (unlikely)
